llowing them to become more confident and gain self-sufficiency more quickly. Working labs are an effective means to ensure user acceptance and success in performance of job tasks.</li><li><b>Ongoing refresher training </b>on updates, new versions or on demands.</li><li><b>Training documentation</b>: Both end-user training manuals and system guides can be found on the website</li></ul>';//content service oursourcing$_['sv_content_technology'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>E-Business: E-commerce, ERP, HRM, BI, POS, CRM </li><li>Supply Chain</li><li>Development methodology</li><li>Java, PHP, and Database</li><li>Technical architecture</li><li>Design patterns</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_Benefits'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><b>Cost advantages</b>: The same services with same level of quality save up to 60% of total cost.</li><li><b>Profit increase</b>: You can save time, effort, infrastructure and manpower.</li><li><b>Specialized services</b>: You can get expert and skilled services.</li><li><b>Start new project quickly</b>: SunflowerVN can start project right away with the right people and the right environment.</li><li><b>Reducing risk</b>: In outsourcing projects, SunflowerVN manages the risk for you.</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_scrum'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Agile Scrum saves time and money.</li><li>Fast moving, cutting edge developments can be quickly coded and tested using this method, as a mistake can be easily rectified.</li><li>Clear visibility of the project development thanks to frequent updates and meetings.</li><li>Due to short sprints and constant feedback, it becomes easier to cope with the changes. </li><li>Daily meetings make it possible to measure individual productivity. This leads to the improvement in the productivity of each of the team members. </li><li>Issues are identified well in advance through the daily meetings and hence can be resolved in speedily.</li><li>It is easier to deliver a quality product in a scheduled time.</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_rup'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>This is a complete methodology in itself with an emphasis on accurate documentation </li><li>It is proactively able to resolve the project risks associated with the clients evolving requirements requiring careful change request management </li><li>Less time is required for integration as the process of integration goes on throughout the software development life cycle. </li><li>The development time required is less due to reuse of components.</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_java'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Model-View-Controller Architecture </li><li>J2EE Design Patterns: Intercepting filter, View helper, Composite view, Front controller, Value object, Session facade, Business delegate, Data access object</li><li>Diagrams: Use case, class, etc.</li><li>Application tiers and Architecture</li><li>Tecnologies: J2EE, Spring, Hibernate, Struts</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_php'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Web site design and redesign</li><li>Web site maintenance and repair services</li><li>HTML⁄XHTML⁄CSS programming</li><li>PHP⁄MySQL programming/custom programming</li><li>AJAX programming</li><li>E-commerce development and shopping carts</li><li>Content management systems (CMS)</li><li>Domain registration, hosting and support</li><li>Search Engine Submission and page optimization</li><li>Technologies: Symfony, Magento, Opencart, Zend, etc.</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_db'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Database design</li><li>Database development and programming</li><li>database integration and conversion</li><li>Database management and administration</li><li>Database maintenance and support</li><li>Technologies: DB2, My SQL, Oracle, Postgre, AS400</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_why_sun_oursourcing'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Skilled Resources: experienced technical team, practical working environment, continuous training. </li><li>Disciplined Project Management: our delivery methodology assures fulfillment of various industrial requirements. </li><li>Flexible contracts: flexible billing and engagement models</li></ul>';//$_['Request_content'] = '';$_['Documentation_content'] = '';$_['sv_content_why_etl'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Data is everywhere. Providing a consistent, single version of the truth across all sources of information is one of the biggest challenges faced by IT organizations today.</li><li>ETL stands for:<ul><li>Data <b>extraction</b> from source databases.</li><li>Transport of the data & data <b>transformation</b>.</li><li><b>Loading</b> of data into a database.</li></ul></li></ul>';$_['sv_content_smart_etl'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Allows data manipulations across multiple sources:<ul><li>Any database using ODBC on Windows.</li><li>MySQL/PostgreSQL/Oracle/AS/400/SQLServer/IBM-DB2.</li><li>MaxDB (SAP DB), SAP R/3 System (ProSAPCONN plugin).</li></ul></li><li>Graphical tool performs the typical data flow functions like <ul><li>  reading, validating, refining, transforming, writing data to</li>   <li>a variety of different data sources and destinations.</li>  </ul></li>  <li>Modern, Standards-based Architecture:  <ul><li>Allows remote monitoring of the running ETL processes through a web browser.100% Java with broad, cross platform support.</li><li>Repository-based providing easy re-use of queries and transformation components</li> <li>along with structured management of models, connections, logs,...</li></ul></li></ul>';$_['sv_content_when_etl'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Application integration, lets say SmartBizPOS-Sync integrate between SmartBizERP & SmartBizPOS.</li> <li>Exploration of data in existing databases (tables, views, etc.),   let"s say SmartBizAlerts (send email/SMS to do internet marketing).</li> <li>Export of database(s) to text-file(s) or other databases.</li> <li>Import of data into databases, ranging from text-files to excel sheets.</li> <li>Data migration between database applications.</li> <li>Information enrichment by looking up data in various information stores (databases, text-files, excel sheets and more).</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_uc_application_integration'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>SmartBizPOS-Sync is a data sharing and integration between ERP & POS where:<ul><li>ERP is the central repository of the data: products, customers, taxes, orders...</li><li>POS has the ability to operate with the master data downloaded from ERP and   to upload orders created by the sales activity of POS.</li>  </ul></li><li>How to share and integrate data between ERP & POS:<ul ><li>The ERP-REST-WebService operates on Business Objects in ERP.</li><li>Synchronize data:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#005c8f">&bull;</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ERP --> POS: products (& product attribute), business partner, price, inventory, tax...<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#005c8f">&bull;</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;POS --> ERP: orders, ...</li><li>How to run ETL transformations and jobs:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#005c8f">&bull;</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Option 1: manually run using graphical tool. <br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#005c8f">&bull;</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Option 2: scheduled in batch mode to be run automatically at regular intervals.</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_uc_exploration_data'] = 'UC Exploration data';$_['sv_content_uc6'] = '<ul class="BossListContent">	<li>Spoon<ul>	<li>is a graphically oriented end-user tool to model the flow of data from input through transformation to output. One such model is also called a transformation</li></ul></li>	<li>Pan<ul>	<li>is a commandline tool that executes transformations modelled with Spoon</li></ul></li>	<li>Chef<ul>	<li>is a graphically oriented end-user tool used to model jobs. Jobs consist of job entries such as transformations, FTP downloads etc. that are placed in a flow of control</li>	</ul></li>	<li>Kitchen<ul>	<li>is a commandline tool used to execute jobs created with Chef</li></ul></li></ul></ul>';// product$_['marketing_automation_name'] = "Marketing Automation";$_['sale_automation_name'] = "Sales Forces Automation";$_['customer_support_name'] = "Customer Support";$_['marketing_automation'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><b>Multi-Channel Campaigns</b> centralizes the development, execution and monitoring of campaigns across multiple channels. It provides detailed views into campaign effectiveness and defines campaign routing and approvals to ensure buy-in across the organization. Company can also benchmark campaigns.</li>									<li><b>Email Marketing</b> allows marketing managers to identify the correct target for a given campaign and track the response rates once a campaign is executed. Monitoring campaign ensures offers reach the targeted audience.</li>									<li><b>Lead Management</b> gives marketing professionals the tools to manage prospects and existing customers. They can qualify and track leads from multiple campaigns and hand them off to the correct sales representative. Our system ensures prospects lists are valid and marketing offers are coordinated.</li></ul>';$_['sale_automation'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><b>Contact Management</b> consolidates contacts into a single location and associates accounts with sales opportunities, account information and customer case information.</li>										<li><b>Opportunity Management</b> allows your team to close deals faster by sharing consistent sales information, tracking deal progress, and recording deal-related interactions.</li>										<li><b>Account Management</b> capabilities provide a single view of customers across products, geographies, account, and status. In one single page, users see not only account information, but all associated sales opportunities, contacts, activities, history, cases and quotes.</li>										<li><b>Forecasting</b> gives sales representatives and managers the ability to generate accurate forecasts based on sales data. Managers can create, assign and edit quotas for their team, roll-up forecasts across individuals and teams, and measure forecast accuracy relative to commit amounts.</li></ul>';$_['customer_support'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><b>Case Management</b> centralizes the service history of each customer, allowing for a detailed view of customer requests and responses. Case management metrics allow managers to monitor how cases are handled and to escalate issues to ensure customer satisfaction.</li><li><b>Inbound Email processing</b> allows support organizations to better manage customer support requests through information sharing and routing. With Inbound Email Processing, users can create rules for in-bound e-mails and automatically assign cases to the right customer support representative.</li></ul>';$_['Ecommerce'] = "Ecommerce";$_['Workflow management systems'] = "Content Management System";$_['Marketing Promotions and Tools'] = "Marketing Promotions and Tools";$_['Full Analytics and Reporting'] = "Full Analytics and Reporting";$_['Catalog Management and Browsing'] = "Catalog Management and Browsing";$_['Order Management'] = "Order Management";$_['Checkout and Payment'] = "Payment Gateway";$_['Social networking'] = "Social Network";$_['Internet marketing'] = "Internet marketing";$_['Ecommerce content'] = '	<ul class="BossListContent">		<li><b>Catalog Management and Browsing:</b> Inventory Management with Backordered items, Minimum and Maximum quantities, Simple, Configurable (e.g. size, color, etc.), Bundled and Grouped Products, Virtual Products, Layered / Faceted Navigation for filtering of products, Product comparisons.</li>		<li><b>Checkout:</b> One-Page Checkout, SSL security support for orders on both front-end and back-end, Shopping Cart with tax and shipping estimates.</li>		<li><b>Order Management:</b> View, edit, create and fulfill orders from admin panel, Create one or multiple invoices, shipments and credit memos per order to allow for split fulfillment, Email Notifications of Orders.</li>		<li><b>Full Analytics and Reporting :</b> Total Sales Invoiced, Total Sales Refunded, etc.</li>	</ul>';$_['Workflow management systems content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Engine of an e-commerce website.<ul>	<li><b>Product management :</b> organized and structured products.</li>	<li><b>Orders processing</b></li>	<li><b>Publish content in specified template on website</b></li>	<li><b>Products interactively purchasing</b></li></ul></li></ul>';$_['Marketing Promotions and Tools content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><strong>Marketing Promotions and Tools</strong>: Flexible Coupons (pricing rules) with ability to restrict to stores, customer groups, time period, products, and categories, Multi-Tier Pricing, Bundled Products</li></ul>';$_['Full Analytics and Reporting content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><strong>Full Analytics and Reporting</strong>: Total Sales Invoiced, Total Sales Refunded, etc.</li></ul>';$_['Catalog Management and Browsing content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><strong>Catalog Management and Browsing</strong>: Inventory Management with Backordered items, Minimum and Maximum quantities, Simple, Configurable (e.g. size, color, etc.), Bundled and Grouped Products, Virtual Products, Layered / Faceted Navigation for filtering of products, Product comparisons</li></ul>';$_['Order Management content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><strong>Order Management</strong>: View, edit, create and fulfill orders from admin panel, Create one or multiple invoices, shipments and credit memos per order to allow for split fulfillment, Email Notifications of Orders</li></ul>';$_['Checkout and Payment content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><strong>Payment gateway</strong>: integrated with multiple gateways<ul >	<li><b>ATOS / SIPS Payment</b></li>	<li><b>Nganluong.vn Payment</b></li>	<li><b>Google Checkout Payment</b></li></ul></li></ul>';$_['Social networking content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><b>Social networking:</b> a method of ecommerce in which consumers in a social networking environment.<ul>	<li><b>Product information sharing :</b> Users communicate and aggregate information about product, price, deal</li>	<li><b>Blog :</b> create and feed blog content on social networking</li>	<li><b>Customer support via social networking</b></li>	<li><b>Sharing events, activities information on Social networking</b></li></ul></li></ul>';$_['Internet marketing content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent">	<li><b>Search engine marketing (SEM)</b></li>	<li><b>Email marketing</b></li>	<li><b>SMS marketing</b></li></ul>';$_['Admin Module'] = "Admin Module";$_['Personal Information Module'] = "Personal Information Module";$_['Employee Self Service Module'] = "Employee Self Service Module";$_['Leave Module'] = "Leave Module";$_['Time And Attendance Module'] = "Time And Attendance Module";$_['Benefit Module'] = "Benefit Module";$_['Performance Module'] = "Performance Module";$_['Admin Module content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>The part of the system where the HR Manager or other appointed personnel perform all <b>system administration</b>  tasks. Security issues are taken care of through this module as well by defining user rights. <ul ><li>Configure LDAP for user domain</li><li>Define Users and group</li><li>Configure and subscribe for E-mail Notifications</li></ul></li></ul>';$_['Personal Information Module content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>This core module maintains all relevant <b>employee related information</b>. Information captured in this module is utilized by all other modules‚ thus eliminating data redundancy. <ul ><li>Personal information (Date of birth, SSN, nationality, ethnic race etc.)</li><li>Payment details (Pay Grade & Salary)</li><li>Employee reporting structure (Assign Supervisor)</li></ul></li></ul>';$_['Employee Self Service Module content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li><b>Employee self service</b>  is a powerful tool providing employees of the company with the ability to view relevant information such as personal information‚ updating personal information with web - enabled PC without having to hassle the HR staff. </li> <li>The functionality of this module spans through the entire system‚ making information available anywhere‚ anytime. Of course all information is subject to company defined security policy‚ where everyone can only view the information he / she is authorized to. Time and cost saving effects from this solution are tremendous.</li></ul>';$_['Leave Module content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>A comprehensive <b>leave management module</b> with extensive possibilities of defining leave types and more. It caters for all applications and approval processes and is able to display information on leave entitlement balance history etc.	<ul>		<li>Receive auto notification e-mails after performing leave related operations</li>			<li>Accumulated annual leave</li>		<li>View Leave Summary of all employees in one screen</li>	</ul></li></ul>';$_['Time And Attendance Module content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>The <b>time tracking</b> module offer functionality enhances the organization performance by eliminating paperwork and manual processes associated with time and attendance needs.<ul><li>Finger printer integration</li><li>Administration and management of your own and your subordinate timesheets</li> <li>Define organization customers and projects</li> </ul></li></ul>';$_['Benefit Module content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Integrated platform to manage String. Covers medical and welfare benefits with possibilities to define new benefits by type provider and several other areas. Assigning benefits to employees happens in a variety of ways individually designation-wise or other.<ul><li>Payroll Management</li><li>Payslip generating and exporting to file</li><li>Employee Hospira (HSP) Summary</li> </ul></li></ul>';$_['Performance Module content'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Another natural attachment to HRM. While simplifying the <b>performance review</b> process you can communicate the key performance indicators for each job title allowing the employees to understand and achieve your expectations.</li></ul>';//demo$_['demo_description']='<h3 class="DetailTitle" id="product_title">SmartBiz-Suite Demos</h3>                <p class="Text4">                    The SmartBiz Suite is designed and developed to highlight the functional and technical capabilities of ERP, POS, BI, and HRM. They are fast and efficient solutions proving comprehensiveness and adaptability to meet your unique needs in a cost effective way.                </p>                <p>Please choose from the demos below for an inside look at the compelling advantages of SmartBiz Suite.</p>';$_['demo_select']='<label><b>Show:</b></label>			        <select id="demo_filter" style="width:207px;">			            <option value="all">All demos</option>			            <option value="erp">Enterprise Resource Planning</option>			            <option value="pos">Point of Sales</option>			            <option value="hrm">Human Resource Management</option>			        </select>';$_['demo_title_erp']=' <th><p>Enterprise Resource Planning</p></th>		                        <th><p>Username/Password</p></th>		                        <th><p>Link</p></th>';$_['demo_title_sales']='Sales and CRM';$_['demo_content_sales']='Drive profitable client interactions: Prices, sales orders, shipments, invoicing, volume discounts, commissions, CRM, etc.		                                <ul class="ProList_do">										<li>Maximum flexibility and adaptability</li>										<li>Multi-store retailers</li>										<li>Integrated with POS</li></ul>';$_['demo_title_Procurement']='Procurement Management';$_['demo_content_Procurement']='Minimize acquisition costs, maximize supplier collaboration: Rates, purchase orders, goods receipts, invoice registration and accounting, purchase planning, etc.										Fully integrated with:										<ul class="ProList_do">										<li>Financial Management</li> 										<li>Accounting</li>										<li>Warehousing</li></ul>';$_['demo_title_Warehouse']='Warehouse Management';$_['demo_content_Warehouse']='Optimize inventory and customer satistfaction: Warehouses and bins, warehouse units, lots, serial numbers, packages, labels, receipts and deliveries, movements between warehouses, inventories, stock valuation, transport, etc.							<ul class="ProList_do">							<li>Inventory in your organization to always be up to date</li>							<li>Correctly valued stock</li>							<li>Synchronization and control of the stock in the shop floor</li></ul>';$_['demo_title_Receivable']='Receivable Payable';$_['demo_content_Receivable']='<ul class="ProList_do"><li> Generation of debt payments (from invoicing)</li><li> Issue of debt payments</li><li> Management (cancellation, merging and division) of accounting documents. Remittances (according to bank records)</li><li> Issue of cash accounts. Multi-cash account</li><li> Cash account journal (cash audit). Cash account entries by type Expenses, Receipts, Balance, Deposits, Bills, Order (for cash payment on delivery note: possibility of recovering expenses before invoicing. Automatic generation of entries for cash payments and payments on delivery note</li><li> Bank statements. Portfolio issues selection assistant</li><li> Manual liquidations. Other expenses (payroll, taxes, etc.)</li><li> Cash account reports, bank, debt payments by position</li></ul>';$_['demo_title_Financial']='Financial and Accounting';$_['demo_content_Financial']='Be in control of your finances top to bottom: Chart of accounts, accounts, budgets, taxes, general accounting, accounts payable, accounts receivable, bank accounting, balance sheet, P&L, fixed assets, etc.							<ul class="ProList_do">							<li>Increase in productivity is due to the financial department</li>							<li>Accounting Solution</li>							<li>Internationalization</li></ul>';$_['demo_title_Project']='Project and Service Management';$_['demo_content_Project']='Drive project profitability: Projects, phases, tasks, resources, budget, expenses and expense invoicing, related purchases, etc.							Define: 							<ul class="ProList_do">							<li>Services</li>							<li>Resources</li>							<li>Control all activities</li></ul>';$_['demo_title_Manufacturing']='Manufacturing';$_['demo_content_Manufacturing']='Be in control of all your processes, end-to-end: Plant structure, production plans, BOMs, MRP, manufacturing orders, job reports, costs of production, work incidences, preventive maintenance types, etc.									<ul class="ProList_do">										<li>Complete shaping of the productive structure</li>										<li>Reduce times and optimally product</li>										<li>Provides these key features and benefits for Manufacturing companies</li>										</ul>';$_['demo_title_Core']='Core';$_['demo_content_Core']='ERP delivers a superior user experience by combining web-based simplicity with practical features that drive productivity and user satisfaction						<ul class="ProList_do">						<li>Alerts, Email, SMS</li>						<li>Linked items, Dimensional Reporting, Compatibility and Sharing, tree, Multi</li>						<li>Modular, Easily configurable, Roles, Auditing</li></ul>';$_['demo_title_pos']='<th><p>Point Of Sales</p></th>             <th><p>Username/Password</p></th>             <th><p> Link</p></th>';$_['demo_title_hrm']='<th><p>Human Resource Management</p></th>             <th><p>Username/Password</p></th>             <th><p> Link</p></th>';$_['demo_title_hrm_hrm']=